nodes.text: Le Projet T-65 (English: Project T-65) is a roleplaying adventure published in issue 27 of the French gaming magazine Backstab in February of 2001. The roleplaying statistics provided were compatible with the roleplaying game created by Wizards of the Coast. The adventure was set up to take place some months after the establishment of the Galactic Empire and detailed a Rebel plot to retrieve prototype T-65 X-wing starfighters from a base on the planet Séléann.
